normalization process of relations between Israel and Arab
countries, to protest Israel's refusal to continue the peace
process with Palestinians. Palestinian leader Yasser Arafat said
that his people are facing "a state of war" and called on Arab
countries to help stop Israel from "Judaizing" Jerusalem. 
