<HEADLINE> Albania Offers to Probe Boat Accident With Italy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, March 30 (Xinhua) -- The Albanian government said today
that an investigation group should be formed immediately to
investigate the sinking of an Albanian refugee boat in the
Adriatic last Friday, which killed 83 people.
</P>
<P>
Albanian Foreign Minister Arijan Starova put forward the
proposal in a letter to his Italian counterpart Lamberto Dini here
today.
</P>
<P>
Starova said last Friday's tragedy could have been avoided.
</P>
