Albania expressed regret over Italy's decision to use naval
ships for patrol operations before the two countries signed a
protocol on patrol at sea.
</P>
<P>
The Albanian government demanded the investigation group should
be made up of Italian, Albanian and international experts.
</P>
<P>
According to Albanian reports, an overloaded Albanian refugee
boat bound for Italy from its southern port of Vlora collided with
an Italian navy vessel about 30 miles away from the Italian
Brindisi port.
</P>
<P>
More than 13,000 Albanian refugees have reached Italy since
tension escalated in Albania earlier this month. 
