imports from Victoria because of the recent anthrax scare and may
extend the ban because of new outbreaks in New South Wales.
</P>
<P>
The Canberra Times
</P>
<P>
-- The Howard government is likely to face a political
challenge over plans to allow mergers between Australia's four
major banks and two largest insurance companies.  
</P>
